Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.79,0:01:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新发明的脚丫践踏者总算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My new Tootsie Trampler is finally complete
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.92,0:01:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于要变成踩别人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last, I will be the stomper
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不再是被别人踩的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not the stompee
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.97,0:01:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像来客了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we have company
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先把你刮下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's exfoliate you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.36,0:01:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy moly macarooney
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, son
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.17,0:01:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ma?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pa?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  你换了新显示器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, is that a new monitor?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好会撩我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You charmer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  恋爱脑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Romeo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们怎么会买得起这种豪华大车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you afford this ridiculous monstrosity?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你妈中彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your ma and me won the lottery
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以就搬到大城市去住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we moved to the big city
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.90,0:02:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟我们高贵到不穿裤子的儿子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like our too-fancy-for-pants son
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还特地请了管家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got ourselves a butler
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您的痰盂  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your spittoon, madam?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来参观一下豪车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want a tour of the vehicle?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not really
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很高档
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real classy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很奢华吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Purty fancy, ain't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得看你怎么定义很奢华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That depends on your definition of pretty and fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱这新买的房车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our new homestead on wheels
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣食住行要用的又全又好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has all the creature comforts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.06,0:02:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如给埃莫用的这个丝绒食槽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this velvet feeding trough for Elmer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它现在可以在奢侈品里打滚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:52.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, he can wallow in luxury
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用滚泥巴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,instead of filth
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  埃莫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Elmer
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put me down
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.07,0:03:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有个并排茅房  适合晚上浪漫几下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a side-by-side outhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for them romantical evenings
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.33,0:03:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再者  空间还够给整个痞家住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plus, there's room for the whole Plankton clan
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们要过来看望多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So how long are you visiting for?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是七  五
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seven, five
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是三分钟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe three minutes?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要留下来  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to stay, son
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们踏上了你的老路子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're following your lead
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己开了家餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and starting up our own restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,714)}薯之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Spud Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in the wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜猜卖的什么菜品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what's on the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜  土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, potatoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来你偷看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You done peeked
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们卖土豆三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got tater sandwiches
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土豆蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spud cakes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜榨土豆汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our fresh squeezed tater juice
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖给小朋友玩的土豆气球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just for the kids, tater balloons
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有压轴好戏  土豆惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the coup de grace, Spud Surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,克莱图斯表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Cousin Cletus
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁说到惊喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say surprise?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我新换的显示器也就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So much for my new monitor
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好归好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但也太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's also stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不会有谁愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's going to
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来这种只卖土豆的餐厅吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,eat at a restaurant that only serves potatoes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potatoes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.83,0:04:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家店只卖土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this place sells nothing but potatoes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Potato?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.05,0:04:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,街对面新开了一家土豆馆子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a new potato restaurant across the street
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.05,0:04:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不会拒绝土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never say no to a starchy tuber
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过去吃土豆吧  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run to the potatoes, Sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要拿这个去买土豆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need this for spuds
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's everybody going?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每道菜品都来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of everything, please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大堆土豆  皮多来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bunch of potatoes, with extra peel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.08,0:05:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, dear?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大众都是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are idiots
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:30.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1256,284)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走啊  拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.62,0:05:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不要富含蛋白质的蟹黄堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like a nice, protein-packed Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.17,0:05:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sorry, bro
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里得去补充碳水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Larry needs to carbo load
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weirdo
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最后一位客人也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was me last customer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以借机利用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can work this to my advantage
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生意今天不太好吗  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Business a little slow today, Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个薯之霸把我客人全吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Spud Bucket has siphoned off all me customers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.74,0:05:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家人新开的餐厅害你停业了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My family's new restaurant has put you out of business
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如把秘方给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may as well just give me the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正你也用不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got no use for it now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boyo, come here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你赢了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You win, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然大家再也不想吃蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Since no one wants Krabby Patties anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我秘方也就一文不值了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me formula is worthless
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这一文不值的秘方在手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this worthless formula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能统治世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can take over the world
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你统治世界的计划不也一文不值了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make your plan for world domination worthless, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.03,0:06:31.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:31.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  带我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, take me home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, muffin
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚引发了一连串的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just sent a series of events in motion
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题马上都可以因此解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that will soon solve all our problems
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么关掉那家破烂薯之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I going to shut down that stupid Spud Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就打电话找卫生检查员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call the health inspector?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他每周都会关停我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He shuts us down every week
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  你可真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, you're a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你是我造的  所以我是双倍天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And since I built you, I'm a double genius
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村卫生局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom Health Department
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家公共场所闹满了害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This joint is completely infested with vermin
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且害虫甚至还在制作食品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The vermins are even preparing the food
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh my
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家餐厅的评级可不应该是A
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This restaurant doesn't deserve an A
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是个AAA+
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It deserves a triple A plus
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是睦邻友好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right neighborly
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢先生大方资助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And thank you, sir, for your generous donation
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生局慈善基金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:47.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the Health Inspector Benevolent Fund
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我随时都可以帮助弱势群体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always ready to help the less fortunate
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想要客人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you want customers, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就送你们个客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a customer
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, son
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你带了什么来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you got there?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你带了开店大礼  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought you a restaurant warming present, Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  贪吃暴客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold, the Insatiable Bulk
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吃的多得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all you can eat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can eat this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can eat all of this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can eat this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can eat--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  薯之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Spud Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非谢谢你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I just have to thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Patrick feller
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我见过最会做土豆泥的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the Jim dandiest tater masher I ever did see
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情进展比我预期的还要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Things are going even better than I hoped
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱你不择手段的样子  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love when you get all Machiavellian, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有一大堆土豆要运到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a load of potatoes for the, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spud Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也有快递
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a delivery, too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire in the hole
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种弹片薯条比普通薯条还要好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This tater shrapnel is better than Frenchy fries
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们开的垃圾薯之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your awful Spud Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毁了我统治世界的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has ruined my plans to conquer the world
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你就来帮我们干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you come work for us?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯之霸可是家族产业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Spud Bucket is a family business
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是家族一份子啊  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're family, son
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我搞不了破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can't sabotage 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消灭不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,annihilate 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也压制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or squelch 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒不如加入得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might as well join 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份土豆特餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Spud du Jour
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做出大家都想吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cooking food that people really want to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实还让我挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,actually makes me pretty happy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的土豆  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your tater, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.98,0:10:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问一下  这个奇怪的土豆加了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what is in this peculiar potato?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是痞式土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a Potato a la Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稍微加了一小撮海霸糊增添风味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With just a pinch of chum for flavor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然是主厨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the chef?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快放下土豆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone, put down your potatoes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.83,0:10:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板在下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton is in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.27,0:11:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我们的开的土豆馆子死得很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess our tater restaurant is a big fat failure
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有得必有失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You win some and you lose some
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,克莱图斯表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cousin Cletus
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你再来一份惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another surprise, please
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, son
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要出发去买橄榄球队了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're off to buy a football team
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果我的秘方还是有点价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turns out me formula's worth something after all
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在谁输了呢  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's the loser now, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁说到惊喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say surprise?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.02,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,不要逗我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:57.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,598)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1268,738)}礁石影院
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love going to the movies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,428)}零食
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黏黏的地板让我心平气和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sticky floors make me feel grounded
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:18.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114,210)}爆草花
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要你看这部电影了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for you to see this movie, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好笑到不能再好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the funniest thing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这辈子我都没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen in your life
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这么一段情节  里面这个角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's this one part where this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来两份套餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two combos, please
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴着顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is wearing a hat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要剧透  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No spoilers, Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:33.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,462)}普鲁登斯恋爱记
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,普鲁登斯恋爱记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Prudence in Love"?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不是很好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound funny
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.02,0:12:36.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  确定来对电影院了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:36.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, are you sure we're in the right theater?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你  普鲁登斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you, Prudence
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是  纳撒尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I you, Nathaniel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我更爱你  普鲁登斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I love you more, Prudence
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我就稍微更爱你一点  纳撒尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I love you slightly more than that, Nathaniel
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不兴比啊  普鲁登斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not a competition, Prudence
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但如果真的在比  我就快赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if it were, I'd be winning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也太甜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not funny
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只不过你的笑声太有感染力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But your laughter is so infectious
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那时  多年以来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just then, all the years
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长期的过度大笑终于付出了代价
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of excessive laughing finally took their toll
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.86,0:13:22.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝的爱笑骨就此卡在了高挡位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:22.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and SpongeBob's funny bone got stuck in high gear
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真没那么好笑  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not that funny, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你笑什么笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是情节片  不是搞笑片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a melodrama, not a comedy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快滚啊  爱笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a hike, Chuckles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看这家伙有多离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you believe this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.59,0:13:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整场电影下来都在那样子笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,laughing all through the movie like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is making all that noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  爱笑男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, laughing boy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带着你的笑声滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take your hardy har hars outside
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么我笑得停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why can't I stop laughing?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,憋住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hold it in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,憋气就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just hold my breath
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,194)}帽子
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你戴着这顶帽子漂亮极了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look fantastic in that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这叫漂亮是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I look fantastic, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.49,0:14:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没在嘲笑你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing at you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真的很喜欢那顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really like that hat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛奶撒了你都哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're crying over spilled milk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:07.17,注释,,0,0,0,,[ cry over spilled milk：后悔无用 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(582,436)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能赶到厨房去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, if I can just make it to the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不会有谁听到我在笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nobody will hear me laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  麻烦你进厨房去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, kindly get in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从我的脸上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And off of my face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your face?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脸哪好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so funny about my face?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么好笑的  不关你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing funny about your--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.96,0:15:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,face
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我反倒要笑你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I laugh at you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别听他胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to him
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里不会有谁听到我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody will hear my laughs in here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要吃东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm eating here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家餐厅为什么在笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is the restaurant laughing at us?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的笑声恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your little laughing prank
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我客人全吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just scared away all the customers
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,解释清楚  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, boyo
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在笑我的脸  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's laughing at my face, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没在笑你  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing at you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都没笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing at anything
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, what do I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想点别的什么好事  别笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of happy thoughts and just knock it off
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒犯到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am offended
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人来接我菲菲的单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no one here to take my Fifi's order
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千分万分对不起  上流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gold-plated sorries, Lady Upturn
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就会给你接贵宾专用订单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will take your very important order right away
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need an ambulance
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我遭遇了不幸  你竟然还敢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you laugh at my misfortune
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.38,0:17:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  马上解雇这个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, fire this cretin at once
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You heard her
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你啥时候不笑不犯傻了再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back when you're not a giggling idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't come back?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  我不是故意要笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs, I'm not laughing on purpose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在嘲笑你  菲菲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's laughing at you, Fifi
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  菲菲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fifi
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to hide
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样我的笑声就不会伤及无辜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That way, my laughter won't hurt anyone else
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一片黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's dark
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不到东西就没得笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If there's nothing to see, there's nothing to laugh at
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.61,0:18:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天要对机器人动手术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today, we will be operating on a robot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.53,0:18:16.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:16.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Robot
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.99,0:18:17.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:17.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How exciting
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What will they think of next?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先开始拧松第一颗螺栓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will begin by loosening the first bolt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,护士  扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse, wrench
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is really on tight
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,护士  海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse, sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手术室里禁止大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laughing is not allowed in the operating room
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是医生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the surgeon now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是医生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the surgeon now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是医生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the surgeon now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.98,0:18:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fascinating
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:58.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(892,242)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is not funny
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1622,508)}通缉\N爱笑疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,488)}墓地
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cemetery
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墓地里面没什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing funny in a cemetery
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是就在这里度过余生好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just live the rest of my life here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clowns?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.93,0:19:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上有两种小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are two kinds of clowns in this world
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皮笑肉不笑的小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,clowns that are only laughing on the outside
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及肉笑皮不笑的小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and clowns that are only laughing on the inside
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪鼻小丑皮笑肉也笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sparkle Nose the Clown was both
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此成为了明星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that's what made him a star
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好庄重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So solemn
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得回避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should leave
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我坐在尸体上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy herring, I'm squatting on a corpse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别坐我胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you get off my chest?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're alive?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然还活着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm alive
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是生前葬礼  全让你搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a living funeral, and you're ruining it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.82,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 生前葬礼：在世时为自己举办的葬礼 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.03,0:20:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没在笑你  闪鼻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing at you, Sparkle Nose
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就从你胸口上下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just get off of your chest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对花环上的花粉过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm allergic to wreath pollen
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃啊  他要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese it, he's going to blow
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把我的小丑葬礼变成了笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You turned my clown funeral into a joke
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原谅我  闪鼻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sparkle Nose
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:02.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1488,382)}禁止游荡
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几小时后  可怜的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hours later, poor SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,依然笑得停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,still could not stop laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的嘴笑到合不拢  张得特别大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:09.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And his laughing mouth got so big
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,占满了一整张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it took over his whole face
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经笑累了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of all this cackling and chuckling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的好想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel more like I want to--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:23.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,494)}七大洋影院  正在放映\N悲泣  最悲伤的电影
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,悲泣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Weep"?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最悲伤的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The saddest movie ever"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一开始是电影害我笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A movie started my laughing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再看一部应该就不会再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe a movie can stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.23,0:21:42.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:42.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.71,0:22:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也笑得停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't stop laughing either?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了  宝贝孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not, dearie
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的爱笑骨好多年前就卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My funny bone got stuck years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时我跟你一样大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I was your age
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的爱笑骨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your funny bone?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们全家都会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It happens to everyone in our family
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.43,0:22:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要为自己的笑声自豪  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be proud of that laugh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.19,0:22:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵家就应该要笑对生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To be a SquarePants is to laugh loud at life
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我一起哈哈大笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy a good laugh with me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.78,0:22:26.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:26.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Grandma
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.28,0:22:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种悲情电影总能逗得我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These tearjerker movies always crack me up
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爆米花吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all out of popcorn
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下悲剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's a tragedy
